                                            <ol> <h3 class="title">Notas</h3> <li class="footnote " id="footnote1-10485_002_027"><a name="-10485_002_027"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote1-10485_002_027">1.</a></span>
					<p class=""><span class="emphasis">Enseñanzas de los Presidentes de la Iglesia: José Smith</span>, 2007, pág. 109.</p>
				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote2-10485_002_027"><a name="-10485_002_027"> </a>
